headline: A Fresh Look at Cencora (COR) Valuation as Shares Rally 8% in the Past Month
summary: Cencora (COR) shares continue to climb, gaining around 1% in the past day and up over 8% for the month. Investors seem to be weighing the company’s strong revenue and net income growth in light of broader market trends. See our latest analysis for Cencora. Cencora’s momentum is clearly building, with a 1-month share price return of 8% and the stock now up over 48% year to date.
